dct_title_s: Map of Adelaide and suburbs shewing streets and allotments
dct_description_sm: Set of Adelaide town plans showing cadastral information along with tramways, railways and roads closed. Map Library has sheets 1-9, 12. "Compiled from available sources, but owing to incomplete data in some instances, accuracy is not guaranteed."
dct_creator_sm: South Australia. Office of the Surveyor General
